00:03:24,970 --> 00:03:32,570
♪ Since by man came death

2
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:36,560
- Have you eaten anything?
- No.

3
00:03:36,810 --> 00:03:40,980
Hey, look, what is this, a picnic? Come on.
Let's go, man. We got ten minutes to go.

4
00:03:42,380 --> 00:03:48,380
♪ Since by man came death

5
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:51,790
- Punch me out, man.
- You got it.

6
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:35,580
Any word from the LAPD intelligence,
if there is such a thing?

7
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,120
- Not yet, sir.
- Of course not.

8
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:42,130
Because we're a covert
anti-terrorism team that is so secret...

9
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:44,210
that when we snap our
fingers nothin' happens!

10
00:04:55,890 --> 00:04:58,060
Sheriff's department?
Airport police?

11
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:01,020
Still waiting. But Interpol
insists he's in Tripoli.

12
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:04,650
Yeah, well, you-you trust... You trust
that billion-dollar satellite, okay?

13
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:07,860
I'll trust a ten-dollar snitch
at this point.

14
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:12,200
- Sean, look...
- What?

15
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:15,120
Why don't you just give 'em
a little break, okay?

16
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:18,960
We'll take a break
when the case breaks, okay?

17
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,840
♪ Hallelujah

18
