22
00:05:41,230 --> 00:05:42,980
♪ Hallelu... Hallelu...
Hallelujah

23
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:47,150
♪ For the Lord God
Omnipotent reigneth

24
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,990
♪ Hallelu... Hallelu...
Hallelu... Hallelu... Hallelujah

25
